public class FIPAManagementOntology
extends Ontology
implements FIPAManagementVocabulary

This class represents the ontology defined by FIPA Agent Management specifications (document no. 23).

The actual Ontology object representing the FIPA-Agent-Management-ontology is a singleton and is accessible through the static method getInstance()
